data.title: Draft Nights
data.meta_description: Two weeks until the day, NBA Draft people of the world. Consider this a quick look back. Because looking forward is the right direction right now. Of the 15 players below who finished the 2013-14 season on the team, exactly six were originally drafted by the Bucks: Henson, Sanders, Antetokounmpo, Ilyasova, Wolters, Sessions. Based on where they were selected, each of the six was a nice value choice. Now for some draft history, with a fun draft class fact for each.
